If your chat account has unconsumed coins or uncollected earnings, all the earnings will be frozen from the date you submit the account deletion, and the operation is irreversible.
data.cancel.hint6: 5. The mobile phone number bound when registering an account needs to wait 90 natural days after deletion before registering or binding again. Each mobile phone number can only be bound to one account. If you need to change the binding, you need to delete the account or unbind or bind to other accounts after a specified period of time after unbinding; and the maximum number of binding accounts for a single mobile phone account is 3 times , if you bind more than 3 times, you will not be able to bind the phone number if you change it.
